        "name": "Temporal Distortion",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "text": "You share some of your own temporal distortions with a foe, altering their mind and body unpredictably as they\u2019re thrown backward or forward in time. Roll 1d4. On a 1, the foe becomes clumsy; on a 2, it becomes enfeebled; on a 3, it becomes stupefied; and on a 4, you choose which condition applies.",
